<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.2.10">
<l>kāvip perunīr vaṇṇaṉ kaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>mēvit tikaḻuṅ kūṭa lūrmēl</l>
<l>kōvait tamiḻāl kaliyaṉ coṉṉa</l>
<l>pāvaip pāṭap pāvam pōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When [you] sing this song composed by Kaliyaṉ in Tamil,</l>
<l>This series on Kūṭalūr where Kaṇṇaṉ,</l>
<l>The color of blue lilies and the great sea, dwells and shines,</l>
<l>[All] misfortune departs.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
